{"type":null,"faqId":49496,"title":"通过 U 盘方式连接","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"通过 U 盘方式连接\"XE \"连接电脑\"XE \"在电脑和手机 SD 卡之间传输文件\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>背景信息</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>当手机中插入了 microSD 卡时，您可以将手机用作 U 盘，在 microSD 卡与电脑之间进行文件传输。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>通过 USB 数据线将手机连接到电脑。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>从状态栏处向下滑动，打开通知面板，将“USB已连接”设置为“U 盘存储”。在电脑端，系统将自动安装驱动程序。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作结果</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>安装完成后，电脑将识别手机为 U 盘。点击电脑中新出现的盘符可以查看手机中 microSD 卡上的文件。</span>\n</p>\n<br>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5240","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294488000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":230,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}